subject: Re:  COMMONWEALITH BANK OF AUSTRAL
body:
Good morning Mr. Penelope Phillips,

Thank you for your message. It's quite surprising to hear about this compensation from the BANK OF AUSTRALIA. Could you please provide more details about this panel and how it works? How did my name get included in this list?

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Preston
